<author>nạṣf ṣbḥy, nạṣf ṣbḥy</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kyf wạ̉nt ạlḥbyb .. yhwy̱ qlby swạk
 (fạ̉nt gẖdẖạʾ nfsy .. qṣd ʿmry rḍạk)2

[C1]
   ạlqrạr- lk rby jmlty .. ạ̉gẖly̱ mạ fy ạlḥyạẗ
   lk tbry fḍty .. lk nfsy yạ ạllh

[V2]
 2- kyf wạ̉nt ạlmjyb .. ạ̉rjw rby swạk
 (fạ̉nt tgẖny ḥyạty .. tʿṭy ḥsb gẖnạk)2

[V3]
 3- kyf wạ̉nt ạlnṣyb .. ysẖbʿny swạk
 (fạ̉nt tkfy ḥyạty .. lạ ykfyny ạ̹lạk)2</lyrics>
<title>kyf wạ̉nt ạlḥbyb</title>
</song>